# Common Threats to AI Models

Organizations should understand the threats that directly target machine learning models.

| Threat | Description |
|------|------|
| Model Theft | Unauthorized copying of AI models |
| Model Tampering | Modification of model parameters or behavior |
| Model Poisoning | Injection of malicious updates during training |
| Model Extraction | Reverse engineering through repeated queries |
| Unauthorized Access | Unapproved access to model repositories or APIs |
