Following deployment, automated monitoring detects an unauthorized attempt to replace the production model with an unapproved version. The integrity verification process immediately blocks the deployment, alerts the security team, and preserves the trusted production model.

By implementing comprehensive model security controls, the organization protects its intellectual property, maintains trustworthy AI operations, and strengthens its Artificial Intelligence Management System.

