# Relationship Between Secure AI Operations and ISO/IEC 42001

ISO/IEC 42001 requires organizations to monitor, maintain, and continually improve AI systems throughout their lifecycle.

Secure AI Operations supports ISO/IEC 42001 by helping organizations:

- Protect AI services.
- Maintain AI reliability.
- Manage operational risks.
- Strengthen AI governance.
- Improve resilience.
- Support continual improvement.

Secure AI Operations should be integrated into:

- AI lifecycle management.
- AI monitoring processes.
- AI risk management.
- Information security management.
- Incident management.
- Change management.
- Business continuity planning.

